Disk Inventory X is a disk usage utility for Mac OS X (10.2+). It shows the sizes of files and folders in a special graphical way called "treemaps".\
\
If you've ever wondered were all your disk space has gone, Disk Inventory X will help you to answer this question.\
\
Please refer to http://www.cs.umd.edu/hcil/treemap-history/index.shtml for further information about treemaps.\
